Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要往这边去了  再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  回见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女性公敌  放弃抵抗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊  樱井？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罪犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这个人到底做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是都晕过去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对罪犯不需要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不  我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}劳驾{\r}\NExcuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,White is...pen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}新干线要怎么乘坐{\r}\NHow can I take a Shinkansen？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}有什么特别的事情需要我做吗{\r}\NIs there anything special I have to do？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…是说到了新干线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}要搭乘新干线的话{\r}\NTo take a Shinkansen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}你需要新干线特急券和普通乘车券各一张{\r}\NYou need limited express ticket and a normal one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}如果你需要帮助  可以去找售票处{\r}\NIf you need some help, there is a ticket office over there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海  多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英语什么的  给我好好学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为铁道脑的妨碍  我记不住英语单词
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩处罪犯还要写检讨  难以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用铅笔  用圆珠笔写哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能重写了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连这么琐碎的事情都得写上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你吧  把那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  我才不想输给男生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  为什么还把人给搞晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服住他不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打晕他不是更方便处理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是反而麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是偶尔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵  有什么我可以帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  不过不要紧  我一个人搞的定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把字写错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三行的「待」写成了「侍」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是些啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光名字根本想象不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是鱼肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚼劲不错的  一入口会让人以为是肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蚕豆汤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地中海一带还是挺常见的菜式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地中海啊  真想通过西伯利亚铁路去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条线路似乎不到地中海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说为什么你们也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也想来这里吃吃看  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是绝佳的团队合作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没夸你  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是高山你不适合来这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樱井你就适合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵  你到底要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推荐各位试试主厨之选的午餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来札沼的OJT是在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  这套制服合身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错…就这点感受？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我是桐生铁道高中的高二生  札沼麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙各位平时照顾高山君了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像娃娃一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件制服真合适
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是铁道高中学生的话  应该也是铁道迷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的是电车的声音和车站的发车音乐之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的音铁对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁道高中的全都是些像高山这样的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说也没有高山君那么奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  来份鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠背正常  座位正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  可以坐下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点脏也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也这么玩过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次一起在教室的时候还真被吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桌子正常  椅子正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然这样叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指差呼唤确认是司机的基础啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大家都爆笑起来了  但我觉得真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真地以列车司机为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以后会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得下去吗  公安队什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  顺其自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  那位樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种人  是不是更适合做公安的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢  有她在治安反而会变差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天到晚折腾来折腾去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不知道她在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭田小姐不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋里的柴油机在阻碍工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是今天捡获失物的统计表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要我来帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  小海同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  嗯  这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后点击这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点  点击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下落不明？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起制作来电铃声的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做薰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她昨天晚上开始就失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要到哪个车站去采集声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去以后  就再也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么打电话都没有接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了哪个车站呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是就那样去旅行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那样  至少会联络一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别见外了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫薰的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的就是从昨天开始所有的报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被卷入了在首都圈发生的事故的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会有一些消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都听好了  对方是众所周知的激进团体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公安机动队  出动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是和以前一样鸡飞狗跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现今为止还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是至少有些线索的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请其他班的人帮忙怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再努力试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得帮助有困难的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们公安的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚公安队的人出发了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公安的工作果然很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过那些人是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君也在做那样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…有时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些东西希望你确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  等下再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个铃声…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是薰的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个手机是在哪里发现的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位小朋友捡到的  好像是在玩的时候发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母就送过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说不知道在哪里捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有照片什么的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通话记录呢  怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易得到的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要知道哪怕蛛丝马迹的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,语音文件呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰的话  也许留下了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的录音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吵  过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海  还有其他的语音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这个的话  没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能从手机中留下的异味里嗅出是哪个车站吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是喜欢铁道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种程度的技能  赶紧学会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼  知道什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么眼前是大海啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国铁鹤见线  海芝浦站
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站台面对京浜运河  是很罕见的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然语音文件里只有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能听到拍打岸壁的波浪声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有制动试验所发出的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只有折返的车站才有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能录下电车和海浪声音的国铁车站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有海芝浦站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连波浪的声音都听得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为札沼的耳朵很灵敏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰是在这里被卷入事件里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  在这周围？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里除了公园  没有许可是不能出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劫持着女性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能长时间乘坐电车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底搜寻这条线路沿线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新芝浦那边也找下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人找到了  地点是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  不要久留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站起来吗？  扶稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种制服  是警察吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了  是铁道公安队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  为什么会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们带着薰快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为代理班长  我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说被逮捕的是违法贩卖药物的团体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰是碰巧到了交易现场  才被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤好像也不重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立功了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是只有夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一群有趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  说不定喜欢上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是今天出院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  只是以防万一才入院的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  多亏了高山和其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢什么的就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君变了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点变帅了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路平安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特急「舞者」号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由使用国铁183系特急型电车运行的特急「天城」号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和使用153系急行型电车运行的急行「伊豆」号统和后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随新型直流特急型电车185系投入运用而诞生的特急列车
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  接下来请老老实实听我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RAIL WARS!  第四话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许喜欢上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了  欢迎来到鹿岛乃亚的舞台！
